As self-appointed sheriff, judge and mayor, Silk Hat now rules the town with a bloody and merciless fist. Meanwhile Bumper, a friend of Bob (also known as U.S. Marshal Black Diamond), is carrying a tidy sum of cash when he is waylaid and robbed in Thunder Basin by none other than Silk Hat. Suspecting something is amiss, Bob adopts the guise of Black Diamond and rides to Thunder Basin, where he demands an audience with Silk Hat. Through treachery, Silk Hat manages to inflict a flesh wound that renders Black Diamond unconscious. Will Black Diamond perish at the hand of Silk Hat, who leers down at him, gun in hand?
